2.00	Razorblade_Romance	Razorblade Romance	Razorblade Romance is the second studio album by HIM, released on 19 December 1999 in Finland and 24 January 2000 in the rest of Europe - except for the UK, where it was released 15 May 2000. It was produced by John Fryer and recorded at Rockfield recording studios in Wales by John Fryer and Paul Read. All songs and lyrics on the album, with the exception of Chris Isaak's "Wicked Game", are composed by Ville Valo.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/9a/Rbr.jpg/220px-Rbr.jpg
